      "content": "i feel like it's more than just a \"debate\" though. if the goal of history is to be accurate, then wouldn't including those voices just be making the curriculum more factual and less biased? it seems like the people calling it an \"agenda\" are just trying to avoid the uncomfortable parts of history.",
